The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 03 August 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guest is Jack Bolinsky, president of Products of Nature Inc., on his efforts to remain in business despite the FDA's efforts to shut his operation down due to his ability to beat the prices of certain FDA-cleared medicines.
